Framework

Next.js app router

State

Zustand or Redux

Realtime

WebSocket events

Rendering

virtualized tables

lazy loading

Performance

streaming UI updates

skeleton loaders

edge caching

13) Super Admin UX Differentiator

Platform Brain Map

Interactive graph showing:

tenants

agents

workloads

connections

Zoomable like a galaxy map.

Allows:

click → inspect

drag → reassign resources

hover → performance stats

